Switch to ros_to_python_type_map

This is just a performance optimization. No need to re-compute the
python types over and over.

ros_to_python_type_map was computed like this:

```python
for (python_type, ros_types) in python_to_ros_type_map.iteritems():
    for ros_type in ros_types:
        if ros_to_python_type_map.has_key(ros_type):
            ros_to_python_type_map[ros_type].append(python_type)
        else:
            ros_to_python_type_map[ros_type] = [python_type]
```
